{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's playing there, and people sent to give him money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they say, oh, that's an idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's start singing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they'll give us money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they start singing, and, of course, they're being chased away by policemen or by-- also by this organ grinder, because they make a lot of noise and they don't know actually how to sing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sing-- their voices are too soft and too-- it's too weak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It doesn't make an impression on anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they fall asleep, and they think, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they fall asleep, and comes in the sparrow, cat, and dog and start to tell them, the only thing you can do, we have to organize it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to organize it with all the schoolchildren, and we are going to unite with the all the schoolchildren and we are going to sing the next day.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then we'll be strong enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they do it-- and being chased away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they get money from the grown ups, who are also, of course, children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the organ grinder takes the money and runs-- and tries to run away, and the children chase him, take the money back again, and everything is OK.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They have the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are going to buy the milk, and the-- and the moral of the story is that if you unite, nobody can do us anything, not even an organ grinder.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who in the end, is by the way, being persuaded also to sing with the children as not to be revengeful or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they say this story-- the end is like if you unite, and if you stick to the truth and are not afraid, we're going to-- to overcome anything.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
